Available Packages
Name       : xfce4-fsguard-plugin
Arch       : i386
Version    : 0.4.0
Release    : 2.el5.centos
Size       : 46 k
Repo       : extras
Summary    : Filesystem-Guard plugin for the Xfce panel
URL        : http://goodies.xfce.org/projects/panel-plugins/xfce4-fsguard-plugin
License    : BSD
Description: A little Xfce plugin, which checks the free space on the chosen
           : mountpoint frequently. It displays 4 different icons and a message
           : box, depending on the free space. The amount of free disk space is
           : visible in a tooltip. If you left-click on its icon, it opens the
           : mountpoint directory in the file manager.

